1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=Saat Aku Bertemu Denganmu=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episod 4=

3
00:00:16,600 --> 00:00:18,239
Tuan Muda Luo,
awak orang berpangkat.

4
00:00:18,239 --> 00:00:19,839
Kenapa awak pergi ke Biro Pintu

5
00:00:19,839 --> 00:00:20,760
jadi konstabel bawahan?

6
00:00:21,079 --> 00:00:22,199
Bukankah lebih baik

7
00:00:22,199 --> 00:00:24,320
berseronok di tempat hiburan ini?

8
00:00:24,320 --> 00:00:25,760
Itu awak silap.

9
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:27,839
(Luo Wuxia, anak keluarga Luo)
Sebagai satu-satunya waris lelaki Luo,

10
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:28,800
aku memang ditakdirkan

11
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:30,800
jadi konstabel terhebat di dunia.

12
00:00:31,120 --> 00:00:32,560
Apa yang wanita macam awak tahu?

13
00:00:33,079 --> 00:00:35,679
Tapi Tuan Luo tak tahu ilmu bela diri, kan?

14
00:00:36,920 --> 00:00:38,320
Duit saja yang aku perlukan, kan?

15
00:00:38,520 --> 00:00:40,190
Apa yang duit tak boleh selesaikan?

16
00:00:40,479 --> 00:00:41,679
Kalau tak boleh diselesaikan,

17
00:00:41,759 --> 00:00:43,679
maknanya kau tak bayar cukup.

18
00:00:48,712 --> 00:00:51,350
(Hu Lie, Pusaran Hitam)

19
00:00:53,840 --> 00:00:54,679
Apa pula sekarang?

20
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:57,240
Nak rompak aku?

21
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:58,240
Baik.

22
00:00:58,520 --> 00:01:00,280
Ambil saja semua di belakang.

23
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:05,519
Tapi dengar sini.

24
00:01:06,120 --> 00:01:07,079
Kau boleh ambil duit,

25
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:10,040
tapi jangan lambatkan aku lapor ke Biro Pintu.

26
00:01:10,799 --> 00:01:11,799
Biro Pintu?

27
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:15,280
Aku paling benci konstabel.

28
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:17,280
Oleh sebab kau kaki tangan Biro Pintu,

29
00:01:17,439 --> 00:01:19,200
hari ini ajal kau sampai!

30
00:01:20,319 --> 00:01:21,000
Tangkap dia!

31
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:22,640
Berani kau!

32
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,079
Kau tahu siapa aku?

33
00:01:24,079 --> 00:01:25,079
Kau tahu siapa kakak aku?

34
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:26,239
Kau tahu siapa datuk aku?

35
00:01:26,500 --> 00:01:27,480
Dia Pesuruhjaya...

36
00:01:27,500 --> 00:01:28,319
Turun dari situ!

37
00:01:28,319 --> 00:01:28,959
Biro itu!

38
00:01:35,375 --> 00:01:38,000
(Kubu Angin Hitam)

39
00:01:45,462 --> 00:01:47,512
(Poster Buruan)

40
00:01:50,787 --> 00:01:53,637
(Maruah Seluas Langit)

41
00:01:54,650 --> 00:01:56,920
(Luo Wushuang,
Timbalan Biro Pintu)

42
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:58,170
Jadi kau Pusaran Hitam.

43
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,519
Siapa kau?

44
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:01,239
Sejak tahun ke-10 Wanli,

45
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,000
kau kuasai Kubu Angin Hitam,

46
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,599
rompak tak terkira pedagang.

47
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:07,640
Kau rampas perak rasmi tiga kali,
culik 21 wanita.

48
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:08,319
Kakak!

49
00:02:08,319 --> 00:02:10,680
Dengan 133 nyawa di tangan kau,

50
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:13,000
kau mengaku bersalah?

51
00:02:16,159 --> 00:02:17,800
Kalau kau tahu rekod aku sangat,

52
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,759
kau masih berani datang seorang diri?

53
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:23,000
Tak takut kau ditelan hidup-hidup di sini?

54
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:25,719
Siapa kambing, siapa harimau?

55
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:27,319
Itu belum tentu.

56
00:02:27,919 --> 00:02:29,000
Bunuh dia!

57
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:45,837
(Maruah Seluas Langit)

58
00:02:45,837 --> 00:02:47,350
(Poster Buruan)

59
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:05,319
Luo Wushuang, Timbalan
Unit Lapangan Biro Pintu,

60
00:03:05,319 --> 00:03:06,490
melapor balik ke ibu pejabat.

61
00:03:06,500 --> 00:03:07,100
(Pesuruhjaya Luo Shixun)

62
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,120
(Pesuruhjaya Luo Shixun)
Salam hormat, Pesuruhjaya.

63
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:10,319
Shuang, kau dah balik.

64
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:11,680
Datuk.

65
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:18,039
Kau pimpin pasukan selamatkan Wuxia

66
00:03:18,420 --> 00:03:19,680
dan tumpaskan Kubu Angin Hitam.

67
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:22,560
Bahagian Personel putuskan
untuk beri anugerah pada kau.

68
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,390
Kau dinaikkan tiga pangkat.

69
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:26,120
Terima kasih, Pesuruhjaya.

70
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,000
Di mana Wuxia?

71
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,000
Dia tak balik dengan kau?

72
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,240
Kena tunggu dia.

73
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:34,100
Katanya menunggang terlalu letih,

74
00:03:34,150 --> 00:03:35,879
jadi dia berkeras
balik naik kereta kuda.

75
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,120
Akan ambil beberapa hari lagi.

76
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:38,439
Datuk,

77
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:40,240
kenapa datuk

78
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,319
panggil aku balik?

79
00:03:41,439 --> 00:03:42,439
Urusan peribadi.

80
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,120
Urusan peribadi?

81
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,360
Apa dia?

82
00:03:48,599 --> 00:03:50,639
Datuk aturkan pertemuan jodoh untuk kau.

83
00:03:51,199 --> 00:03:52,080
Pertemuan jodoh?

84
00:03:54,919 --> 00:03:57,639
Ayah, ayah tahu Chang saja
yang aku nak kahwin.

85
00:03:57,639 --> 00:03:58,319
Tapi...

86
00:03:58,879 --> 00:04:00,599
Dengar dulu siapa orangnya

87
00:04:00,599 --> 00:04:01,919
sebelum kau buat keputusan.

88
00:04:01,919 --> 00:04:02,800
Aku tak peduli.

89
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,520
Walaupun dia puteri sekali pun,

90
00:04:04,610 --> 00:04:05,639
aku tak berminat.

91
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,960
Orangnya Wushuang.

92
00:04:08,919 --> 00:04:09,520
Siapa?

93
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,159
Luo Wushuang.

94
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,360
Jangan risau, Chang.

95
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,879
Aku takkan kecewakan kau.

96
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,000
Kenapa?

97
00:04:45,319 --> 00:04:48,040
Awak nak ambil balik
hadiah yang awak bagi?

98
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:50,079
Aku tak pernah kata nak ambil balik.

99
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:52,110
Aku cuma risau ia buat kau tak selesa

100
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,800
masa kau nak tidur.

101
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,680
Ini "ubat penahan sakit" aku.

102
00:04:58,199 --> 00:04:59,199
Aku kena pegang ini.

103
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:02,879
Chang, aku minta maaf sangat.

104
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:05,240
Keluarga aku buat ini pada kau.

105
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,759
Sepatutnya aku yang minta maaf.

106
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:13,879
Kalau pak cik aku tak cari pasal
dengan orang yang salah berniaga,

107
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:17,240
kakak kau dan aku
takkan diculik.

108
00:05:19,639 --> 00:05:20,639
Sejak kebelakangan ini,

109
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,399
aku banyak fikir pasal kita.

110
00:05:24,050 --> 00:05:25,879
Aku percaya untuk dua orang bersama,

111
00:05:26,759 --> 00:05:28,240
keikhlasan paling utama.

112
00:05:29,959 --> 00:05:31,519
Tak patut ada rahsia antara kita.

113
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:36,639
Jadi...

114
00:05:38,399 --> 00:05:40,000
Buyu, aku...

115
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,120
Chang, kau betul.

116
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:44,079
Dalam hubungan,
tak boleh ada rahsia.

117
00:05:44,519 --> 00:05:45,839
Sebab itu aku perlu minta maaf.

118
00:05:46,759 --> 00:05:48,319
Aku kena jujur dengan kau.

119
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,000
Aku...

120
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,000
Cakaplah.

121
00:05:56,319 --> 00:05:56,879
Aku...

122
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:00,710
Ayah aku cuba jodohkan aku
dengan Luo Wushuang.

123
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:04,759
Siapa itu?

124
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:09,079
Dia cucu Pesuruhjaya kita.

125
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:13,079
Tapi jangan risau.

126
00:06:13,279 --> 00:06:15,920
Wushuang dan aku dah macam adik-beradik
sejak kecil.

127
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:19,279
Lagipun, dia sangat sombong.

128
00:06:19,639 --> 00:06:21,639
Tak mungkin
dia berminat pada aku.

129
00:06:22,639 --> 00:06:23,439
Percayalah.

130
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:25,240
Aku akan pastikan hal ini selesai

131
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,460
dan jelaskan semuanya pada dia.

132
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,680
Kalau tak, ayah aku akan terus campur tangan.

133
00:06:30,639 --> 00:06:32,519
Ini yang awak nak beritahu aku?

134
00:06:33,650 --> 00:06:34,639
Jangan salah faham.

135
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,360
Cuma kau seorang dalam hati aku.

136
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,439
Awak ni kelakar.

137
00:06:38,620 --> 00:06:39,680
Awak dah cakap benar,

138
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:41,120
mana mungkin aku salah faham?

139
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,120
Awak memang terbaik.

140
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:46,600
Baiklah, Chang.

141
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:47,519
Awak tengah pulih.

142
00:06:47,519 --> 00:06:48,480
Awak kena rehat.

143
00:06:49,959 --> 00:06:50,480
Jom.

144
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:51,959
Tidurlah.

145
00:06:51,959 --> 00:06:53,160
Aku akan duduk sini dengan kau.

146
00:07:19,662 --> 00:07:20,183
Berhenti!

147
00:07:26,975 --> 00:07:29,712
(Puan Seribu Tangan, Lin Xin'er)

148
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:32,439
Saudara pengembara, apa urusan saudara?

149
00:07:33,879 --> 00:07:36,959
Tinggalkan kereta, kau akan hidup.

150
00:07:37,439 --> 00:07:38,040
Cik,

151
00:07:38,839 --> 00:07:40,399
ini milik Sihai Escort.

152
00:07:54,639 --> 00:07:56,720
Ratu Pencuri Selatan, Lady Seribu Tangan!

153
00:08:09,399 --> 00:08:09,920
Bergerak.

154
00:08:17,362 --> 00:08:18,321
Ke Ibu Kota.

155
00:08:19,012 --> 00:08:21,411
Dah tiba masa jumpa ketua
Perikatan Persilatan...

156
00:08:23,439 --> 00:08:25,600
Perguruan Sacred Hand.

157
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,680
Pelayan! Bawa arak!

158
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:31,920
Sekejap lagi!

159
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:32,679
Buyu,

160
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:35,480
kau tahu kenapa

161
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,440
kita jumpa hari ini?

162
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:39,799
Aku dengar orang tua kita

163
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:41,799
nak jodohkan kita.

164
00:08:43,519 --> 00:08:46,159
Nampak sangat mereka
betul-betul rancang.

165
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:47,919
Shuang,

166
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:49,559
kita macam saudara.

167
00:08:49,700 --> 00:08:51,399
Tak mungkin kau
minat aku.

168
00:08:51,559 --> 00:08:52,480
Pelayan! Sini!

169
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:53,559
Datang!

170
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:58,320
Kalau aku tak berminat,

171
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,399
aku takkan datang.

172
00:09:01,399 --> 00:09:02,190
Kalau begitu, berhenti minum.

173
00:09:02,919 --> 00:09:03,919
Kau makan saja.

174
00:09:07,159 --> 00:09:07,879
Cuba yang ini.

175
00:09:09,519 --> 00:09:10,440
Buyu!

176
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:13,680
- Mak Cik!
- Kebetulan!

177
00:09:13,919 --> 00:09:15,039
Mak Cik pun ada di sini?

178
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,879
Buyu, siapa ini?

179
00:09:19,159 --> 00:09:19,919
Buyu,

180
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:22,039
sejak bila citarasa kau
jadi seteruk ini?

181
00:09:22,039 --> 00:09:23,240
Macam mana kau boleh duduk sini

182
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:25,399
berbual dan makan dengan perempuan sebarangan?

183
00:09:26,919 --> 00:09:27,679
Apa kau cakap?

184
00:09:27,919 --> 00:09:28,679
Apa aku cakap?

185
00:09:28,679 --> 00:09:29,559
Ada aku cakap apa-apa?

186
00:09:29,559 --> 00:09:30,679
Aku baru nak buka mulut,

187
00:09:30,679 --> 00:09:31,840
kau dah melenting.

188
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:33,039
Seramnya!

189
00:09:33,559 --> 00:09:34,679
Budak perempuan, dengar sini.

190
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,320
Kalau mulut kau setajam ini,

191
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:38,200
lelaki semua akan lari.

192
00:09:38,919 --> 00:09:40,759
Kau... aku...

193
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:42,919
Kalau macam itu,

194
00:09:43,559 --> 00:09:45,399
Chang kita memang yang terbaik.

195
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:46,679
- Dia lemah lembut, beradab.
- Chang...

196
00:09:46,679 --> 00:09:47,759
Dan juga memahami.

197
00:09:48,399 --> 00:09:50,320
Patutlah kau beria nak kahwin dengan dia.

198
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,320
Tunggu, Shuang...

199
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:56,120
Ini mak cik tunang aku.

200
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,320
Dia bukan maksud macam itu.

201
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,200
Oh, tapi memang aku maksudkan.

202
00:10:00,639 --> 00:10:02,559
Aku cuma tak tahan tengok orang

203
00:10:02,559 --> 00:10:04,039
buat-buat kesunyian dan terdesak.

204
00:10:04,559 --> 00:10:05,639
Begini,

205
00:10:05,639 --> 00:10:06,919
aku suruh Mak Cik Yun aturkan

206
00:10:06,919 --> 00:10:08,960
berpuluh lelaki untuk kau jumpa.

207
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:11,840
Jadi kau takkan ada masa lagi

208
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:13,559
nak melekat pada tunang orang!

209
00:10:13,559 --> 00:10:14,000
Mak Cik!

210
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,559
Tengok, mereka tengah bergaduh.

211
00:10:15,559 --> 00:10:16,320
Ada apa?

212
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:17,039
Tak tahu.

213
00:10:18,399 --> 00:10:19,960
Mak Cik, makanlah dulu.

214
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:22,320
Sikit saja, Mak Cik.

215
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,279
Kenapa kau masih duduk sini?

216
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,320
Pergi cari Chang!

217
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:26,480
Yu.

218
00:10:27,279 --> 00:10:28,759
Kalau kau dah ada tunang,

219
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:30,279
kenapa setuju jumpa aku?

220
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:32,720
Wushuang,

221
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:34,279
pertemuan ini

222
00:10:34,279 --> 00:10:35,320
idea ayah aku.

223
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,399
Tapi aku juga nak jelaskan semuanya.

224
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,279
Tiada masa depan untuk kita.

225
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:40,990
Kalau aku menyinggung perasaan,

226
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:42,200
harap kau maafkan aku.

227
00:10:45,919 --> 00:10:47,279
Kamu berdua habiskan makan dulu.

228
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,480
Aku minta diri.

229
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,480
Aku pun pergi.

230
00:10:50,039 --> 00:10:50,559
Buyu!

231
00:10:50,559 --> 00:10:51,840
Jumpa lagi, cik!

232
00:10:52,679 --> 00:10:53,919
Wushuang, perlahan-lahan.

233
00:10:53,919 --> 00:10:54,919
Aku dah bayar.

234
00:10:54,919 --> 00:10:55,480
Silakan.

235
00:11:01,919 --> 00:11:04,480
(Restoran Cuiyun)
Uncang wangi dan loket!

236
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,679
Bagus juga, Mao Buyu.

237
00:11:05,810 --> 00:11:07,890
Kau buat temu janji jodoh
di belakang Chang.

238
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:09,120
Siap dengan seorang timbalan perempuan pula.

239
00:11:09,130 --> 00:11:10,279
Mak Cik, Mak Cik salah faham.

240
00:11:10,399 --> 00:11:11,279
Aku tak ada

241
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:12,559
perasaan cinta pada Wushuang.

242
00:11:12,559 --> 00:11:13,399
Aku boleh bersumpah.

243
00:11:14,039 --> 00:11:15,320
Berhenti berlakon.

244
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:16,120
Kalau kau berani sangat,

245
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:17,480
pergi jelaskan pada Chang kami.

246
00:11:18,570 --> 00:11:19,480
Aku dah beritahu dia pasal ini.

247
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,750
Aku pun tengah nak jumpa dia.

248
00:11:20,919 --> 00:11:21,919
Aku minta diri dulu.

249
00:11:34,639 --> 00:11:35,600
Aku nak cakap satu saja.

250
00:11:35,799 --> 00:11:37,200
Chu Yunchang ialah anak saudara aku.

251
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,519
Jangan ganggu lelaki dia.

252
00:11:39,919 --> 00:11:41,080
Kalau aku tak mahu?

253
00:11:41,919 --> 00:11:43,279
Kalau begitu, aku bagi satu nasihat.

254
00:11:43,559 --> 00:11:44,639
Membawa lampu ke tempat kotor

255
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:45,960
hanya mengundang celaka.

256
00:11:47,325 --> 00:11:48,625
(Restoran Cuiyun)

257
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:54,799
Nimbus Palm!

258
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,404
Kau dari Perguruan Sacred Hand!

259
00:12:00,225 --> 00:12:00,825
Jom!

260
00:12:04,300 --> 00:12:05,214
Plum Blossom Dart...

261
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:07,799
Raja Pencuri!

262
00:12:08,575 --> 00:12:09,216
(Apa?)

263
00:12:09,900 --> 00:12:11,919
(Perguruan Sacred Hand
dan Raja Pencuri)

264
00:12:11,919 --> 00:12:12,890
(menyokong Chu Yunchang?)

265
00:12:19,350 --> 00:12:22,625
♪Dendam dan sesal bagaikan arak pekat♪

266
00:12:22,663 --> 00:12:25,538
♪Teguk saja, lepaskan semuanya♪

267
00:12:26,038 --> 00:12:31,756
♪Cawan kosong buat cinta dan benci kita♪

268
00:12:32,938 --> 00:12:36,258
♪Air mata kaburkan takdir yang tak mampu aku kawal♪

269
00:12:36,388 --> 00:12:39,308
♪Mari minum sampai subuh♪

270
00:12:40,476 --> 00:12:45,716
♪Di sebalik topeng ini, aku takkan berdusta♪

271
00:12:46,938 --> 00:12:49,331
♪Setiap pertemuan semula terasa seperti pertama kali♪

272
00:12:49,331 --> 00:12:52,981
♪Senyum tersembunyi ini takkan pudar♪

273
00:12:53,050 --> 00:12:56,540
♪Satu hati, setia di sisimu♪

274
00:12:56,638 --> 00:12:59,613
♪Hingga ke hujung waktu♪

275
00:12:59,613 --> 00:13:02,988
♪Bulan melakar wajahmu♪

276
00:13:03,175 --> 00:13:06,763
♪Diselimuti awan, kau penuhi hatiku♪

277
00:13:06,763 --> 00:13:13,003
♪Untuk mencari dirimu
dan menepati janji selamanya♪

278
00:13:13,338 --> 00:13:16,553
♪Doa senyap dalam jiwaku♪

279
00:13:16,838 --> 00:13:20,376
♪Menggalas ikrarku di bawah bulan♪

280
00:13:20,663 --> 00:13:23,688
♪Berharap kita takkan terpisah lagi♪

281
00:13:23,688 --> 00:13:26,788
♪Dalam perjalanan menuju selamanya♪

282
00:13:26,788 --> 00:13:30,638
♪Bulan melakar wajahmu♪

283
00:13:30,638 --> 00:13:33,998
♪Diselimuti awan, kau penuhi hatiku♪

284
00:13:34,188 --> 00:13:40,148
♪Untuk mencari dirimu
dan menepati janji selamanya♪

285
00:13:41,225 --> 00:13:50,865
♪Hanya untuk bersama kamu♪

